    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation against the FDA benchmark dataset demonstrates NIH prediction error of 8.3%, within the 15% acceptance criterion. A limitation exists regarding turbulence model performance in low-shear near-wall regions, which affects shear stress predictions at off-design conditions; additionally, the lowest flow-rate operating condition was not fully covered by experimental data. The assessment team considers the risk acceptable and the model credible for the stated COU. Decision: Accepted.",
